---

<div class="affiliate-section">
  <h4 class="affiliate-heading">✦ 旅遊推薦</h4>
  <div class="affiliate-grid">
    {travelLinks.map(link => (
      <a href={link.url} target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" class="affiliate-card"
         style={`--card-color: ${link.color}`}>
        <span class="aff-emoji">{link.emoji}</span>
        <span class="aff-name">{link.name}</span>
        <span class="aff-desc">{link.desc}</span>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h4 class="affiliate-heading">✦ VPN 推薦</h4>
  <div class="affiliate-grid">
    {vpnLinks.map(link => (
      <a href={link.url} target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" class="affiliate-card"
         style={`--card-color: ${link.color}`}>
        <span class="aff-emoji">{link.emoji}</span>
        <span class="aff-name">{link.name}</span>
        <span class="aff-desc">{link.desc}</span>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <p class="affiliate-disclosure">
    💡 這些連結有些是聯盟連結喔！如果你透過它們購買或註冊，我會得到一點點回饋，但不影響你的優惠價格，算是給我繼續創作的動力啦！
  </p>
